* xmessage-1.0.1 (21 Sep 2007)

  21 Sep 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  xmessage-1.0.1.ebuild, +files/Xmessage:
  Initial overlay import. Fix appdefault path in a hackish way, since
